description: I am a developer with 3 years of experience in Java, with knowledge in Spring Boot, Hibernate, Docker, and AWS. I also have expertise in React.js for the frontend. Throughout my journey, I have had the opportunity to create solutions that have positively impacted the lives of many people, making them scalable and responsive for hundreds of users. My main focus is to create software that is not only functional but also intuitive and pleasant to use. I am always seeking ways to enhance my skills.
